About Us

Learn More About Us

Book a Table

Our restaurant is dedicated to bringing you the best of traditional Misal, with a focus on the iconic Maharashtrian dish. We use the freshest and highest quality ingredients to create authentic and flavorful dishes that will transport you to the streets of Maharashtian village. Whether you're a foodie looking for a new culinary adventure or simply seeking a delicious meal, Maher Misal Restaurant is the perfect destination. So, come and indulge in the mouth-watering flavors of Maharashtra at Misal Restaurant.
